      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get the general idea but can u go deeper into the specific roles? like what are neutrophils actually doing during that acute phase versus what lymphocytes are doing in the chronic phase? i need to be able to differentiate their mechanisms if the question asks about cellular activity.",
